snippet.title: TABOO 5 ~ The forbidden fruit merges sweet ~ | Episode 1/ Part 1
snippet.description:
You are a female university student living in the suburbs. Returning from school, a man suddenly attacks you in a dark street. 

You feel the fangs pierce your neck as well as... pleasure. From that night you become his servant.

The fate of story comes to life with the encounter of 5 men. See for yourself, the shape of love beyond the taboo...

🧛🏻‍♂️Choice:

Did you just add me as the third wheel?

•I don't know
•I'd love to!

🧛🏻‍♂️Choice:

Excuse me...!

•No, hold it in
•Wait a second!

🧛🏻‍♂️Choice:

Huh... Who can it be at this hour?

•Answer 💎 ↑❤️↑ Josh
•Ignore

🧛🏻‍♂️Choice:

You'd probably get his information on your own and go see him otherwise 

•I'm terribly sorry! 💎↑❤️↑Josh
•You're such a dependable boss!
